Please notice that this project is only for Desktop Usage.

For EnterpriseLinux Server settings, you do not have to install 3-party repo/rpms. Those trusted packages should be installed only.

This project is a cmdline script which, will finish the installations on XFCE desktop for EL7.

By plan, it works on both CentOS7 and OracleLinux 7

- CentOS Linux release 7.0.1406 (Core) 
- OEL7 //ToDo


It relies on EPEL repo and oracle public-yum, also CentOS base yum repo.

Customized RPMs is located on my server.


